xt":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small drum, slender in the middle:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) accord. to some, (TA,) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"musical instrument called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barobaT","text_ar":"بَرْبَط"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) as occurring in a trad. of 'Alee, in which a command is given to break the thing thus called. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fihorN","text_ar":"فِهْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small stone, such as fills the hand."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","K","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}